		title: "Steam Power"
		icon: {id: "create_steam_n_rails:steam_boiler", Count: 1b}
		description: ["Water Wheels and Windmills have a stress ceiling. The Steam Boiler from Create: Steam & Rails blows past that ceiling — it burns fuel to generate pressurized steam, which drives a Steam Engine that outputs far more SU than any passive source.", "This is the power upgrade that unlocks the faster, heavier Create machines. Build it before you need it."]
