		title: "All Aboard"
		icon: {id: "create_steam_n_rails:steam_locomotive", Count: 1b}
		description: ["Create: Steam & Rails adds functional trains — lay track, place a Station, assemble a locomotive, and it will run a fixed route between stops autonomously. Freight cars haul chests. Passenger cars carry players.", "This is optional, but building a rail line between your base and a distant resource site is one of the better decisions you'll make in the middle game. The train doesn't get tired."]
